      "writtenOn": "2021-07-09T01:37:45Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I went with your suggested factoring. There\u0027s still some nontrivial repetition which bothers me (and we can philosophize over lunch someday; text makes this sort of debate come off louder than it\u0027s meant :-)), but I like the compactness of your sendJSONResponse() concept.",
